| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4488 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ab0a391e-65fb-55ef-a02c-a2c6ff1edb77"
